SetGameOver:
CHECK_ALLEGIANCE 0xFFFF
SVAL 0x1 0x2
BNE 0x1 0xC 0x1 //branch to label 1 if unit is not enemy
ASMC 0x00D391 //game over
GOTO 2
LABEL 1
ENUF 0x9 //allow event to repeat
LABEL 2
NoFade
ENDA

